quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,94,"Wi' so tawii ko onon tan ke…ďata aljanna to laakara njelo…óee maayde so tawii ko on goong…óu…ďe."
  2,95,"∆Āe njelotaako nde muk sabu ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe ngardini , Alla Ombo anndi too√Īoo…ďe …ďee."
  2,96,"Ma a taw ko kam…ďe …ďuri reer…óude he nguurndam e …ďeen renndin…ďe e Alla, gooto he ma…ď…ďe ina yi…ói wuurde duu…ďe ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti wo…ó…óintaa mo lette Alla mo yi'a golle ma…ď…ďe."
  2,97,"Wiy kala gon…óo ga√Īo Jibriilu yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder …ďernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuun…óini defte …óe …ďe njogii ko nde peewal e malu goong…óin…ďe."
  2,98,"Kala gon…óo ga√Īo Alla e malaykaa…ďe Makko e nulaa…ďe Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko ga√Īo heefer…ďe …ďee."
  2,99,"Min njippinii he maa maandeeji la…ď…ďinooji alaa jeddoowo …ói sonaa faasigee…ďe …ďee."
  2,100,"Wolla kala nde …ďe pi…ďi aadi wooda e ma…ď…ďe firtu…ďe mbo accu tan …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe ngoong…óinaani."
  2,101,"Nde Nulaa…óo Alla ari e ma…ď…ďe ombo goong…óina ko …ďe njogii koo, woodi heen sete salii rontii deftere Alla nde wa'i no …ďe nganndaa nii."